snippet.title: Hydro Thunder GO Trailer
snippet.description: We're proud to announce our latest game we've created together with Microsoft Game Studios: Hydro Thunder GO for Windows Phone 7. It's an all-new addition to this high-speed powerboat racing series with new unique content, featuring amazing water physics, gorgeous visuals and over-the-top interactive environments.
